title: Lana Jewelry Narrow Flat Upside Down Gold Hoop Earrings
description:
Take a fresh twist on a traditional hoop and you will be hooked!  Both feminine and flirty, these hoops exude undeniable confidence.  Made of 14-karat gold.  Designed by Chicago designer and founder of the luxe jewelry line Lana Jewelry, Lana Bramlette.   Go glam and channel  your inner celebrity!  

2-1/4 x 2/5 in.
